 width=\"550\"></p><h3>Horseshoe Bend on the Colorado River</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-32.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"344\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Woodlands in the Netherlands</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-33.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"367\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Path in the woods</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-34.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"344\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Aligned</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-35.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"413\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Telatyn, Poland</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-36.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"403\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Morondava, Madagascar</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-37.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"413\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>The Verzasca River, Swiss Alps</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-38.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"413\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Gobi Desert, Mongolia</h3><p><img src=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/ArchitectureArtdesigns-39.jpg\" alt=\"39 Awesome Nature Photos Of Incredible Places\" height=\"365\" width=\"550\"></p><h3>Also check this&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.architectureartdesigns.com/25-of-the-coolest-beaches-in-the-world/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(245, 183, 78);\">25 of the Coolest Beaches in the World</a></h3><p><br></p>
