g>Identity</strong><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/identity-1.png?resize=491%2C254&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"identity\" height=\"254\" width=\"491\"></p><p><strong>Hotels</strong><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hotels-1.png?resize=604%2C264&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"hotels\" height=\"264\" width=\"604\"></p><p><strong>Geohashing</strong><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/geohashing-1.png?resize=604%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"geohashing\" height=\"336\" width=\"604\"></p><p><strong>Game AIs</strong><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/game_ais-1.png?resize=495%2C1013&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"game_ais\" height=\"1013\" width=\"495\"></p><p><strong>Crowdsourcing</strong><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/crowdsourcing-1.png?resize=211%2C382&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"crowdsourcing\" height=\"382\" width=\"211\"></p><p><strong>Context Bot</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/contextbot-1.png?resize=325%2C485&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"contextbot\" height=\"485\" width=\"325\"></p><p><strong>Binary Heart</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://xkcd.com/99/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(188, 54, 10); background-color: transparent;\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/s3.amazonaws.com/production-wordpress-assets/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/binary_heart1.jpg?resize=400%2C438&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"binary_heart\" height=\"438\" width=\"400\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://airbrake.io/account/new/free?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=bottom-post&amp;utm_campaign=Get+Airbrake+For+Free&amp;utm_content=The%20Definitive%20Collection%20of%20XKCD%20Programmers%20Comics\" ta