t I got it for $12 at my local fabric store)</p><p>- Zipper: I used a 22 inch zipper and cut it down to 14 inches. Use a longer zipper if you want your sweater to be able to go more off the shoulder. I got thick YYK brand zipper because I wanted it to be prominent. (~$3)</p><p>- Thread ($2)</p><p><strong>TOOLS</strong></p><p>- Sewing machine</p><p>- Zipper foot</p><p>- Hand sewing needle</p>
